posting_body: This is a 2 Bedroom, 2 Bath, approximately 1023 Sq.
Waters Edge is surrounded by serene park-like landscapes and features wonderful lake views with plenty of green space, where meandering walkways crisscross beautifully groomed courtyards.
You will feel right at home in this comfortable residential setting.
Spacious kitchens feature plenty of counter-space for cooking and your personal touches.

Waters Edge is close to Boeing and just minutes from freeway access to 167 and the fabulous shops at Kent Station where you'll find a movie theater, as well as a number of great restaurants and boutiques.
Workout in our on-site fitness center or unwind in the outdoor pool.
If you are looking for a new community with that brings warm residential comfort, visit Waters Edge.
